lt of their evolution in the context of hierarchical galaxy formation and\nevolution. We predict that proto-GC formation is most prevalent at $2\\lesssim z\n\\lesssim 3$, which could be tested with observations of lensed galaxies using\nJWST.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 May 2019 18:00:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-15"}
