 and reported several issues when\napplying those techniques on a real-world debugging context. Conclusion: The\nmain conclusion of this study is that the idea of an \"interactive\"\nspecification mining rather than a fully automated mining tool is NOT\nimpractical and indeed is useful for the debugging use case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 May 2019 19:39:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-09"}
