t is important, and it significantly affects the spectral\nparameters and the consequential physical interpretations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 May 2019 03:37:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Aug 2019 08:49:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 8 Sep 2019 17:14:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 9 Nov 2019 00:08:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-12"}
